     <div type="to_the_author">
   <head>To the Author.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>VVHen I behold the Author and his Booke,</l>
      <l>With wonder and delight on both I looke;</l>
      <l>Both are so like, and both deserue so well,</l>
      <l>Were I not friend, I in their praise would dwell.</l>
      <l>But since it would seeme partiall, I thinke fit</l>
      <l>To leaue their praises▪ to a better wit:</l>
      <l>But Husband like to this I wish God send</l>
      <l>To those are cha<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1+ letters">
            <desc>•…</desc>
         </gap>t, and to me such a friend.</l>
      <l>Liue each in other, be each others praise,</l>
      <l>Time shall not end your glory with your daies.</l>
   </lg>
   <p>
      <hi>E. Leuenth.</hi>
   </p>
</div>
